The enemy Alistar gave this build a name, called it Raptor Olaf.

Get ZZ rto early because you can use it to keep the lane stable and return to it fast with the Raptor. RG for those engages, OW so that Banner of Command and ZZ'Rot become unstoppable and attack speed and Lifesteal for those danty temfights.
